{"tid":2157653,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"台灣副總統賴清德：香港不會孤單，民主台灣將一直與你們同行！","createTime":"2020-08-15T07:28:13.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-15T07:36:44.000Z","uid":70063,"like":12,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"34f5c0cede0f8399da4aa028ba41e7b1007252f9","tid":2157653,"uid":70063,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-15T07:28:13.000Z","msg":"一個人，一間書店，一輩子堅定的民主信仰。<br />\n　　<br />\n昨晚，來到落腳台灣的銅鑼灣書店－台灣重啟，和林榮基老闆聊閱讀、買書，也關心香港。<br />\n　　<br />\n愛書的林老闆欣賞台灣出版的多元和活力，還向我分享他的私房書單。<br />\n　　<br />\n談到香港的局勢、台灣的未來，我請林老闆向香港的朋友傳達，台灣不會袖手旁觀，會為港人提供必要的協助與關懷。<br />\n　　<br />\n自由的台灣撐住香港的自由，香港不會孤單，民主台灣將一直與你們同行！<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/daW1Wic.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FdaW1Wic.jpg&h=47c19df8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/BKUZHYa.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FBKUZHYa.jpg&h=de39116c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/RQoGWh9.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FRQoGWh9.jpg&h=c4835cd2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/GyLewRt.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FGyLewRt.jpg&h=386a37f5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/dNJPkKN.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FdNJPkKN.jpg&h=6c9919c6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/152472278103133/posts/3730900960260229/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2F152472278103133%2Fposts%2F3730900960260229%2F&d=kJyKEnCePQht%2Ftv3UrQe8ZhbjDs%2B%2F0Yai8vOOt2IPjE%3D&h=7b6c0e78\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/152472278103133/posts/3730900960260229/</a>"},{"pid":"af802bcedd245402ba7eb6900a6ce0af56609641","tid":2157653,"uid":70063,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-15T07:30:29.000Z","msg":"賴清德：就算報紙刊出一張白紙！也要爭取 ＃言論自由<br />\n　　<br />\n前兩天，香港警方以莫須有的罪名，逮捕「壹傳媒」創辦人黎智英、前香港眾志成員周庭等人。<br />\n　　<br />\n但許多香港朋友仍然無畏壓迫，勇敢站出來，排隊搶購蘋果日報，＃就算出白紙都買！以行動支持言論自由，顯示香港人追求民主的堅定決心。<br />\n　　<br />\n中國逮捕的不是黎智英，而是監禁了言論自由；中國摧毀的不是香港自治，而是踐踏民主的價值。<br />\n　　<br />\n人類歷史證明，唯有民主制度，人民的力量才能展現；也唯有百分百言論自由，人民的聲音才能宏亮。<br />\n　　<br />\n台灣走過顛簸的民主改革之路，也經歷過連講話、寫作、出版都不能自由的黑暗年代，現今香港人民所身處的不安，我們感同身受，不會袖手旁觀。<br />\n　　<br />\n面對中國一連串傷害人權的行徑，呼籲同為民主陣營的國家，一起站出來，集結最大力量，透過國際輿論譴責中國鎮壓人權和言論自由的行為，協助港人守護人權和自由。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/152472278103133/posts/3726158107401181/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2F152472278103133%2Fposts%2F3726158107401181%2F&d=kJyKEnCePQht%2Ftv3UrQe8ZhbjDs%2B%2F0Yai8vOOt2IPjE%3D&h=bd176457\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/152472278103133/posts/3726158107401181/</a>"},{"pid":"5c8e096a62f6bc268651adf6135dadd0b752dfc4","tid":2157653,"uid":232157,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-15T07:31:38.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d71a8fe2c18ebbd6c0d289d86009220d6eec40c5","tid":2157653,"uid":70063,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-15T07:31:51.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://twitter.com/ChingteLai/status/1293170759171366913?s=19\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FChingteLai%2Fstatus%2F1293170759171366913%3Fs%3D19&d=kJyKEnCePQht%2Ftv3UrQe8ZhbjDs%2B%2F0Yai8vOOt2IPjE%3D&h=d59ed4df\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FChingteLai%2Fstatus%2F1293170759171366913%3Fs%3D19&h=b9e1f24d\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://twitter.com/ChingteLai/status/1293170759171366913?s=19</a>"},{"pid":"da8c70daea47c92e9b15789a6ddee46f95e4b92c","tid":2157653,"uid":251945,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-1